subSubSection.paragraph:
Diagnosis (modified from
Benavides-Serrato et al . 2011
). Disc (interradial regions) covered by long needleshaped spines and with tubercle-like spines between the long spines; radial shields naked; ventral arm plates square, with depressed distal edge.

